creator: Joust Corp
descriptionHtml:
What is Joust?
Joust is a content (image and PDF) sharing platform with chat functionality. Joust provides features that enable people to share content freely with peace of mind.
Who is it for?
Joust is for anyone (people and companies) who want to share and communicate with confidence that their content is protected against abuse or misuse.
How is it different?
Joust is different in many ways. With Joust, you don’t send an image, you share it. Joust users can share and stop sharing their content at the push of a button. Joust users can apply features such as watermarking, requiring a pin code to view an image, and even setting a geofence for the image. Joust believes in empowering people to take back control of their digital presence.
Does Joust sell my data?
No, Joust does not sell any user data.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Performance improvements
- Easier to find recent notifications
- Able to unsubscribe from all email notifications
- Bug Fixes

title: Joust

creator: Joust Corp
descriptionHtml:
What is Joust?
Joust is a content (image and PDF) sharing platform with chat functionality. Joust provides features that enable people to share content freely with peace of mind.
Who is it for?
Joust is for anyone (people and companies) who want to share and communicate with confidence that their content is protected against abuse or misuse.
How is it different?
Joust is different in many ways. With Joust, you don’t send an image, you share it. Joust users can share and stop sharing their content at the push of a button. Joust users can apply features such as watermarking, requiring a pin code to view an image, and even setting a geofence for the image. Joust believes in empowering people to take back control of their digital presence.
Does Joust sell my data?
No, Joust does not sell any user data.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: - Several internal upgrades to performance and security
